# Runix Hub · Design Vision **0.4 “Astra‑Lite”**

*“Every claim runnable. Every result verifiable. Every explorer welcome.”*

> **Theme tagline:** **Soft‑UI × Pastel‑Bento**
> A crisp, accessible aesthetic that combines tactile Soft‑UI controls with pastel bento tiles—**no blur, no glass**—for maximal clarity and performance.

---

## 0 · The Three Pillars (North‑star)

| Emoji | Pillar                     | Dominant UI Accent / Icon / Motion                 |
| ----- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| 🗂️   | **Versioned Knowledge**    | `primary-500` · `hash` chip · **snap**             |
| 🛠️   | **Composable Models**      | `accent-500` · `flask-run` · **spark-glow**        |
| 🤝    | **Human–AI Collaboration** | `viz-purple-500` · `handshake` · **pulse-success** |

> **Rule:** every primary surface declares its pillar via color **and** emoji.

---

## 1 · Brand Essence

| Axis            | Trait                  | Astra‑Lite Update                                                   |
| --------------- | ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Personality     | **Radical‑rigor**      | Warm pastels + hash badges—zero decorative blur.                    |
| Visual Metaphor | *Layered pastel cards* | Flat cards stack like lab notes; depth via soft shadows, not glass. |
